  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To show that Irbesartan improves endothelial dysfunction and the procoagulant state which are
      thought to be the possible mechanisms, inducing a generalized vasculopathy associated with
      microalbuminuria and vascular events in type II diabetic hypertensive patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
